-- Wal-Mart's Asda says to create 8,000 jobs in UK
-- 
-- Wed Feb 21, 2007 6:09am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/21/us-adsa-jobs-idUSWLB528320070221

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - Asda, the British supermarket unit of Wal-Mart Stores Inc ( WMT.N ), said on Wednesday it would create 8,000 jobs in the UK this year and build a minimum of 18 new stores. 


 Asda, Britain's second-biggest supermarket group, also confirmed in a statement that it will roll-out Asda Living, its non-food operation, to a further 10 sites.